ages/publications/22-07-2012A_%E2%80%98titanic%E2%80%99_electro-mechanical_achievement.pdf_.pdf" class="press-download"><i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <span class="">download pdf</span></a></div></div></div>      <div class="col-12 all new-launch"><div class="card voltas-card voltas-card-press_release"><div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title"><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/25-06-2012_A_coveted_engineering_design_award_for_Voltas%E2%80%99_Co-Gen_VAM.pdf_.pdf" target="_blank">A coveted engineering design award for Voltas’ Co-Gen VAM</a></h4><p class="card-text">The 6th Bry-Air Award for Excellence in HVAC&R (system design) was presented to Voltas recently. The award is in recognition of the outstanding indigenous design of the 1300 TR Co-gen VAM installed at Thyagaraj Stadium in Delhi, for the Commonwealth Games 2010. The design challenge was to maximize capacity while occupying minimum space, due to severe constraints. </p><h6 class="card-overtitle">June 2012, Mumbai</h6><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/25-06-2012_A_coveted_engineering_design_award_for_Voltas%E2%80%99_Co-Gen_VAM.pdf_.pdf" class="press-download"><i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <span class="">download pdf</span></a></div></div></div>      <div class="col-12 all financial"><div class="card voltas-card voltas-card-press_release"><div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title"><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/May_24%2C_2012Voltas%E2%80%99_Consolidated_Financial_Results_for_2011-12.pdf_.pdf" target="_blank">Voltas’ Consolidated Financial Results for 2011-12</a></h4><p class="card-text">The consolidated Sales/Income from operations for the quarter ended 31st March, 2012 was Rs. 1573 crores as compared to Rs. 1671 crores in the corresponding quarter last year. Operating Profit for the quarter was Rs 138 crores as compared to Rs. 145 crores in the corresponding quarter last year.